definition.de:
Das Datum und die Uhrzeit, zu der das Objekt veröffentlicht wurde.
siehe [https://www.w3.org/TR/activitystreams-vocabulary/#dfn-published](https://www.w3.org/TR/activitystreams-vocabulary/#dfn-published)
definition.en:
The date and time at which the object was published.
see [https://www.w3.org/TR/activitystreams-vocabulary/#dfn-published](https://www.w3.org/TR/activitystreams-vocabulary/#dfn-published)
definition.fr:
La date et l'heure auxquelles l'objet a été publié.
voir [https://www.w3.org/TR/activitystreams-vocabulary/#dfn-published](https://www.w3.org/TR/activitystreams-vocabulary/#dfn-published)
definition.es:
La fecha y hora en la que se publicó el objeto.
ver [https://www.w3.org/TR/activitystreams-vocabulary/#dfn-published](https://www.w3.org/TR/activitystreams-vocabulary/#dfn-published)
